snippet.title: Ravenous Devils Launch Trailer - April 29th
snippet.description:
Ravenous Devils are Making Mince-Meat of Happy-Go-Lucky Shoppers on April 29th for Console & PC!
We would like to invite you to wishlist our game if you haven’t already, and remind you to keep an eye out on this page, as we’re set to share all the links for your preferred platform shortly.  
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1615290/Ravenous_Devils/
